---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - LastWave" description="Learn about LastWave, the free tool that turns your Last.fm and ListenBrainz scrobbles into stunning wave visualizations of your music listening trends.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6">
    <h1 class="mb-6 mt-10 font-display text-4xl text-lw-heading">What is LastWave?</h1>
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-lw-muted">
      LastWave is a free tool that visualizes your music listening history as a beautiful wave graph.
      Connect your <a href="https://last.fm" class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim">Last.fm</a>
      or <a href="https://listenbrainz.org" class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim">ListenBrainz</a>
      account to see your top artists, albums, and genres charted over time — the more you listen to
      an artist, the larger their wave on the graph.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-lw-muted">
      Use Spotify, Apple Music, or another streaming service? You can connect it to
      <a href="https://last.fm" class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim">Last.fm</a>
      to start tracking your listening history, then visualize it here with LastWave.
    </p>

    <div class="my-10 h-px w-12 bg-lw-border"></div>

    <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-lw-heading">Who built LastWave?</h2>
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-lw-muted">
      LastWave is written and maintained by <a
        href="https://savas.ca/"
        class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim">Niko Savas</a
      >. Swing by my
      <a
        href="http://last.fm/user/taurheim"
        class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim">last.fm</a
      > profile and say hi!
    </p>

    <div class="my-10 h-px w-12 bg-lw-border"></div>

    <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-lw-heading">Support LastWave</h2>
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-lw-muted">
      Any money donated will go directly to hosting and server costs for LastWave, so that I can
      keep LastWave completely free!
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      <a
        href="https://buymeacoffee.com/nikosavas"
        class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-lw-accent px-6 py-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-lw-bg transition-all hover:bg-lw-accent-dim"
        >Buy me a coffee</a
      >
    </p>

    <div class="my-10 h-px w-12 bg-lw-border"></div>

    <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-lw-heading">Contribute</h2>
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-lw-muted">
      If you're a developer who wants a feature or wants to help develop this tool, please swing by
      this project's
      <a
        href="https://github.com/taurheim/LastWave"
        class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim">GitHub repository</a
      > and submit a pull request!
    </p>

    <div class="my-10 h-px w-12 bg-lw-border"></div>

    <h2 class="mb-4 font-display text-2xl text-lw-heading">Technologies</h2>
    <p class="mb-12 leading-relaxed text-lw-muted">
      Version 4 of LastWave is built using <a
        href="https://astro.build/"
        class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim">Astro</a
      >,
      <a href="https://react.dev/" class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim"
        >React</a
      >, and
      <a
        href="https://www.typescriptlang.org"
        class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim">TypeScript</a
      >. For a full list of dependencies, visit the project's
      <a
        href="https://github.com/taurheim/LastWave"
        class="text-lw-accent transition-colors hover:text-lw-accent-dim">GitHub</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
